This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Information Theory (cs.IT), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), or Numerical Analysis (cs.NA) sub-categories.
